Class HistoryProperty

java.lang.Object
  model.agent.property.Property
      model.agent.property.properties.HistoryProperty

public class HistoryProperty
extends Property

This Property stores the history of the Agent it belongs to. When a Property is changed, mutate(Property) should be called to store the new version.

Author:
W.H. Mook
